		{"id":"135124db8a8e1d21","type":"text","text":"# ***SpacePlacementModel***\n\n\tid: string\n\tstableId: string\n\tspaceId: string\n\tkind: SpacePlacementKind\n\ttargetId: string\n\tx: number\n\ty: number\n\twidth: number\n\theight: number\n\tzIndex: number\n\torder: number\n","x":3700,"y":-140,"width":540,"height":380},
		{"id":"4106fddfd157929b","type":"text","text":"# ***SpaceModel***\n\n\tid: string\n\tstableId: string\n\tname: string\n\torder: number\n\tpages: PageModel[]\n\tplacements: SpacePlacementModel[]\n","x":3000,"y":-480,"width":540,"height":260},
		{"id":"ae6dd8065be6fc4c","type":"text","text":"# ***ProjectComponentStylePresetModel ***\n\n\tid: string\n\tcomponentVariantId: string | null\n\tcomponentStyleId: string\n\tstringValue: string | null\n\tnumberValue: number | null\n\tbooleanValue: boolean | null\n\tunit: StyleValueUnit | null\n\tformat: StyleValueFormat | null\n\tdesignTokenId: string | null\n\tdesignTokenValueId: string | null\n","x":4380,"y":220,"width":540,"height":350},
		{"id":"a1b9e6785f4d3723","type":"text","text":"# ***ProjectComponentPresetModel***\n\n\tid: string\n\tcomponentId: string\n\tstylePresets: ProjectComponentStylePresetModel[]\n","x":4380,"y":-140,"width":540,"height":180},
		{"id":"12bc6f0e362a3bb9","type":"text","text":"# ***Runtime***\n\n```ts\nabstract class Runtime<T> {\n  protected mounted = false;\n\n  mount(target: T): void {\n    if (this.mounted) return;\n\n    this.onMount(target);\n    this.mounted = true;\n  }\n\n  unmount(): void {\n    if (!this.mounted) return;\n\n    this.onUnmount();\n    this.mounted = false;\n  }\n\n  protected abstract onMount(target: T): void;\n  protected abstract onUnmount(): void;\n}\n```","x":-9620,"y":40,"width":760,"height":600,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"6e40f166251a2013","type":"text","text":"# ***ComponentStore***\n\n","x":-2800,"y":1760,"width":760,"height":480},
		{"id":"874c5327027a91c6","type":"text","text":"# ***SelectionRuntime***\n\n- SpaceSelectionController\n    - 한 Space 내부의 선택 상태 관리\n    - placement/page/pageTree 선택\n- SelectionRuntime\n    - 프로젝트 편집 세션 전체의 현재 선택 상태 관리\n    - active space selection을 받아서 Inspector/Navigator/Toolbar가 볼 수 있는 형태로 정리\n- EventBus\n    - Space selection 변경 이벤트 전달","x":-1920,"y":1760,"width":760,"height":480},
		{"id":"bd9ca29608a58940","type":"text","text":"# ***HistoryRuntime***\n\ntype CommandResult = {\n  changed: boolean;\n  changedEntityIds?: ObjectId[];\n};","x":-1080,"y":1760,"width":760,"height":480},
		{"id":"735c3091012e088b","type":"text","text":"# ***UndoRedoRuntime***\n\n","x":-240,"y":1760,"width":760,"height":480},
		{"id":"eabb34d8180c1714","type":"text","text":"# ***InspectorRuntime***\n\n","x":-8120,"y":1760,"width":760,"height":480},
		{"id":"3a7a19a2d2579b04","type":"text","text":"# ***NavigatorRuntime***\n\n","x":-7200,"y":1760,"width":760,"height":480},
		{"id":"13470671b7a7bcd9","type":"text","text":"# ***ToolbarRuntime***\n\n","x":-6320,"y":1760,"width":760,"height":480},
		{"id":"ab04a3f0943461bc","type":"text","text":"# ***CommandBus***\n\n\n```\nclass SelectTargetCommand {\n  constructor(\n    readonly spaceId: string,\n    readonly target: SelectionTarget,\n  ) {}\n}\nhandler가 찾습니다.\n\nclass SelectTargetHandler {\n  constructor(private runtime: ProjectRuntime) {}\n\n  execute(command: SelectTargetCommand) {\n    const spaceRuntime =\n      this.runtime.spaceRegistry.get(command.spaceId);\n\n    spaceRuntime.selection.select(command.target);\n  }\n}\n\n\ncommandBus.register(SelectTargetCommand, new SelectTargetHandler(projectRuntime));\ncommandBus.register(SetZoomCommand, new SetZoomHandler(projectRuntime));\ncommandBus.register(UpdateStyleOverrideCommand\n\n\nCommand는 **무엇을 할지와 대상 id만 가진다.**\n\nCommandBus는 **handler를 찾는다.**\n\nCommandHandler가 **context를 통해 store/runtime을 찾아서 실제 처리한다.**\n\n```","x":-5440,"y":1760,"width":760,"height":880},
		{"id":"e35c3b3a4978281a","type":"text","text":"# EventBus\n\n","x":-4560,"y":1760,"width":760,"height":480},
		{"id":"278f528dc599cd85","type":"text","text":"# ***ProjectStore***\n\n","x":-9120,"y":1760,"width":760,"height":1080},
		{"id":"51072e164105dd70","type":"text","text":"# ***SpaceRuntimeRegistry***\n\n","x":-10420,"y":1720,"width":760,"height":480},
		{"id":"40d7ea11c77666e0","type":"text","text":"# ***SpaceRuntime***\n\n```ts\nclass SpaceRuntime extends Runtime<HTMLElement> {\n  readonly spaceId: string;\n\n  readonly camera: SpaceCamera;\n  readonly renderer: SpaceRenderer;\n  readonly selection: SpaceSelectionController;\n  readonly interaction: InteractionController;\n  readonly measurement: MeasurementStore;\n  readonly scheduler: RenderScheduler;\n\n  constructor(\n    readonly projectRuntime: ProjectRuntime,\n    readonly space: SpaceModel,\n  ) {\n    super();\n\n    this.spaceId = space.id;\n\n    this.camera = new SpaceCamera(this);\n    this.renderer = new SpaceRenderer(this);\n    this.selection = new SpaceSelectionController(this);\n    this.interaction = new InteractionController(this);\n    this.measurement = new MeasurementStore(this);\n    this.scheduler = new RenderScheduler(this);\n  }\n\n  protected onMount(container: HTMLElement) {\n    this.renderer.mount(container);\n    this.interaction.mount(container);\n    this.scheduler.start();\n  }\n\n  protected onUnmount() {\n    this.scheduler.stop();\n    this.interaction.unmount();\n    this.renderer.unmount();\n  }\n}\n```","x":-10480,"y":3120,"width":740,"height":1020},
		{"id":"d0e5c1ce52baaa4c","type":"text","text":"# ***SpaceRenderer***\n\n","x":-10480,"y":4440,"width":740,"height":1020},
		{"id":"d649f136f995c314","type":"text","text":"# ***BackgroundLayer***\n\nz-index: 0","x":-10480,"y":5880,"width":760,"height":440}
	],
